hen supported"},"632":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-26","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"**Home** / **End**: jump to `minValue` or `maxValue` when those props are set"},"633":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-27","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"Stepper buttons are real buttons and follow standard button keyboard activation. Use &#x2A;*`incrementAriaLabel`*&#x2A; and &#x2A;*`decrementAriaLabel`** when the default labels are not enough in your locale or UI."},"634":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-28","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"The input is associated with the visible label and optional description and error content for assistive technologies."},"635":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-29","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Invalid and required states are exposed to assistive technologies when you use `isInvalid`, `errorMessage`, and `isRequired`."},"636":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-30","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Set &#x2A;*`isWheelDisabled`** if the value should not change when the user scrolls with a pointer wheel while the field is focused."},"637":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-31","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Pair &#x2A;*`isInvalid`*&#x2A; with &#x2A;*`errorMessage`** so users get both visual and programmatic feedback."},"638":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-32","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Remember valid steps start from &#x2A;*`minValue`**."},"639":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-33","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Use &#x2A;*`isDisabled`*&#x2A; when the value cannot be changed; use &#x2A;*`isReadOnly`** when the value should be visible but not editable. Do not use them interchangeably."},"640":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-34","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"For currency or units, ensure &#x2A;*`formatOptions`** (and locale) match what users are allowed to type."},"641":{"id":"/docs/components/popover","page_id":"/docs/components/popover","type":"page","content":"Popover","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/popover"},"642":{"id":"/docs/components/popover-0","page_id":"/docs/components/popover","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/popover","content":"The Popover component is an overlay element positioned relative to a trigger element."},"643":{"id":"/docs/components/popover-1","page_id":"/docs/components/popover","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/popover#installation","content":"Installation"},"644":{"id":"/docs/components/popover-2","page_id":"/docs/components/popover","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/popover#props","content":"Props"},"645":{"id":"/docs/components/popover-3","page_id":"/docs/components/popover","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/popover#examples","content":"Examples"},"646":{"id":"/docs/components/popover-4","page_id":"/docs/components/popover","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/popover#basic-usage","content":"Basic Usage"},"647":{"id":"/docs/components/popover-5","page_id":"/docs/components/popover","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/popover#custom-anchor",