ode=\"multiple\"` → `role=\"toolbar\"` on container, `role=\"button\"` + `aria-pressed` per item"},"952":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-57","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"`aria-label` (or `aria-labelledby`) is required on the group container"},"953":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-58","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#aria-support","content":"Icon-only items require `aria-label` on each `ToggleButton`"},"954":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-59","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For grouped contextual actions — two or more closely related actions that belong together (e.g. Bold / Italic / Underline, Align Left / Center / Right)"},"955":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-60","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For compact action grouping — related actions in space-constrained layouts (e.g. Undo / Redo, Zoom In / Out / Reset)"},"956":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-61","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"✅ For multi-select scenarios — when users need to select multiple options simultaneously"},"957":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-62","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For unrelated actions that perform disconnected tasks without shared context"},"958":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-63","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For more than 5 choices — cognitive overload; consider a **Select** instead"},"959":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-64","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ When actions require strong visual distinction (e.g. Save vs. Delete)"},"960":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-65","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ When selecting an option leads to a different page or workflow — use navigation instead"},"961":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-66","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#when-to-use","content":"❌ For mutually exclusive content views (e.g. Monthly / Yearly) — use **SegmentedController** instead"},"962":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-67","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#keep-variants-consistent","content":"Avoid mixing different content types (text-only, icon-only, icon+text) within the same group. Mixing styles creates visual noise and makes the set feel fragmented rather than unified."},"963":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-68","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#balance-label-lengths","content":"Keep button labels of similar length. Large differences in text length cause irregular button widths and make the group appear uneven. Prefer short, concise wording."},"964":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-69","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"Align the group to reflect its relationship to surrounding content:"},"965":{"id":"/docs/components/toggle-button-70","page_id":"/docs/components/toggle-button","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/toggle-button#alignment","content":"**Left** — when the group controls content di